{"tid":310410,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[求行程推薦]黎緊同女朋友去七日泰國","createTime":"2017-07-05T18:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T15:12:59.000Z","uid":14600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"424a55b830aa9d42c6983390b8fc9a9161ef71a4","tid":310410,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:46:48.000Z","msg":"黎緊7月7號同女朋友去七日泰國<br />\n4日芭提雅 3日曼谷<br />\n<br />\n第一日落機返到酒店我諗都大約下晝五點，諗住夜晚搵啲夜市食嘢或者睇下人妖，上網搵到一個地方 叫Mimosa，但唔知好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二日會去Cartoon Network個水上樂園，玩到夜晚就去Rimpa Lapin食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三日BOOK左HopeTrip去格蘭島玩，但未諗到夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第四日起身Check-out 轉曼谷，不過未諗到點過去，炳嫂？ 呢一日朝早仲可唔可以出到去行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？ 同埋唔知當日夜晚做咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後黎緊既三日係曼谷仲未諗好，希望各巴絲出手<br />\n係第七日我地搭下晝5點20分機，由曼谷去DMK大概預幾耐？係曼谷既話Call 炳嫂好定用其他方法？<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各巴打絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無盡感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb72267a4afbed4b97fa3262dc22b2b204dbc8e","tid":310410,"uid":47614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:56:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"47b871a37269bb857359b32bd3230e70355c1d05","tid":310410,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b25d6f1aca8062bee5fc891f0f3c565bcc7a6e","tid":310410,"uid":102197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T19:05:23.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8月尾都