cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後黎緊既三日係曼谷仲未諗好，希望各巴絲出手<br />\n係第七日我地搭下晝5點20分機，由曼谷去DMK大概預幾耐？係曼谷既話Call 炳嫂好定用其他方法？<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各巴打絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無盡感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實炳嫂個rate仲差個BKK地牢間superich <br />\n當然你唔係兌100幾十萬 <br />\n兌1-2萬差唔到好遠<br />\n去過10次到全部都係superich兌 橙色既間野 <br />\n有啲BTS都有 或者pattaya有啲細檔啲rate都靚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b06d0c84864b3635fa43ae28fe3e34c6ba53595","tid":310410,"uid":102197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:24:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6800def174ac96b53d98effa6553ea06d82bcb25","tid":310410,"uid":124799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:29:00.000Z","msg":"GoGoBar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74156023e57a9e0b171f89d9a41531a390c8d240","tid":310410,"uid":14600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T00:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊7月7號同女朋友去七日泰國<br />\n4日芭提雅 3日曼谷<br />\n<br />\n第一日落機返到酒店我諗都大約下晝五點，諗住夜晚搵啲夜市食嘢或者睇下人妖，上網搵到一個地方 叫Mimosa，但唔知好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第二日會去Cartoon Network個水上樂園，玩到夜晚就去Rimpa Lapin食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第三日BOOK左HopeTrip去格蘭島玩，但未諗到夜晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第四日起身Check-out 轉曼谷，不過未諗到點過去，炳嫂？ 呢一日朝早仲可唔可以出到去行下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？ 同埋唔知當日夜晚做咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後黎緊既三日係曼谷仲未諗好，希望各巴絲出手<br />\n係第七日我地搭下晝5點20分機，由曼谷去DMK大概預幾耐？係曼谷既話Call 炳嫂好定用其他方法？<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各巴打絲打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.g